- AD-UserCopy-Tool.ps1 (Copying, Logging, OU)
- Active Directory User Management Script v2.4 (Template-based logic, Logging)
- CopyCreateNewUser.ps1 (Template Export concept, CSV Creation)
- Concept: Applying properties/groups to existing users
- `L-Kennung_Report.ps1` / `L-Kennung_Tabelle.ps1` (Basis for User Export: Filter users, get properties, resolve groups, extract OU, export to CSV)
- `L-Kennung-PWset_V2.ps1` (Specific filter criteria and OU targeting for the `-ExportLKennung` mode)

